{"tid":319660,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"致2017DSE考生低分者","createTime":"2017-07-13T03:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T10:45:10.000Z","uid":632,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9429b3947e2b84d73b8cd2e71f83e518b319dace","tid":319660,"uid":632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十個有九個話自己咩未盡力<br />\n<br />\n個個都考前3大<br />\n考後8大<br />\n放榜i大<br />\n<br />\n想問咩叫盡力<br />\n仲有餘力點解今年唔一早博盡<br />\n放左榜先話未盡力<br />\n咁你啲力留左係邊？留呢有咩用？<br />\n<br />\n如果你地選擇retake就認真諗下呢一年點溫書<br />\n識唔少人得一個月火，過左一個月又打回原形<br />\n第二年又喊住話未盡力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRetake呢條路唔易，得定失就睇你自己<br />\n<br />\n升asso hd 個班 唔好以為咁樣自己就埋左岸<br />\n你地仲係一舊垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真心想讀書既就唔好上個啲濕鳩莊<br />\n奉告一句 識人好緊要<br />\n識人話要asso爆四升大學 最後識左班人上莊 <br />\n畢業後拎住個濕鳩asso搵工先後悔<br />\n<br />\n上莊，玩同前途既priority 自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔好理你個班升到大學 日日玩到癲既朋友/同學<br />\n請你認清自己身分同依加要做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸 過來人 祝大家好運"},{"pid":"66ae0dca788145511886f463b30b7136a8def517","tid":319660,"uid":632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"升到大學仲有大把時間比你玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcee68986e9fad1c5af6d9f5bc0c454ce81263a","tid":319660,"uid":632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0561d3f46535cbdd1a7677bd042a981ff6d14a7","tid":319660,"uid":632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"